OL,6,FA man has been jailed for stabbing
OL,7,Fthree of his family members at a care
OL,8,Fhome in before going on the run.JIzoel
OL,9,FCrudu broke into the residential home
OL,10,Fand attacked two of his victims with a
OL,11,Fknife on 21 December 2022, leaving
OL,12,Fthem with slash wounds to their arms
OL,13,Fand hands.JThe next day in the early
OL,14,Fhours of the morning, the 27-year-old
OL,15,Fwas spotted by another family member
OL,16,Fon West Bromwich High Street.
OL,18,FA fight broke-out between the men,
OL,19,Fbefore Crudu stabbed his third victim
OL,20,Fthree times.
